REPOST @bob___wilson I am happy to announce that Christopher Knowles' exhibition STAND at the Watermill Center will be extended to March 24th 2023.

This survey of over 200 Knowles works is something you need to experience. 

The Watermill Center will soon be announcing Saturday public tour dates for the exhibition for the months of January - March 2023. Visit www.watermillcenter.org soon for more information. 

